OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry. The rest of the night
OL,7,Fwill be mainly dry although rather
OL,8,Fcloudy, perhaps a little light rain
OL,9,Fdeveloping across the Southern Uplands
OL,10,Fat times.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FDry in the morning with
OL,13,Fsome bright spells. Then rain will
OL,14,Fspread southeast during the afternoon,
OL,15,Falthough the far southeast dry until
OL,16,Flater.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,19,Fon Thursday. Unsettled with showers or
OL,20,Flonger spells of rain on Friday and
OL,21,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
